<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200819/ec72654bda2d404fb759009ba9635143.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>动作3、哑铃卧推 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200819/4cbb00a851a44947bd11dcbc898ff2b3.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>动作4、哑铃推举</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200819/145fa713bad241b48c7d2722e9faff21.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>动作5、哑铃硬拉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200819/04c85c355f5c49fba59a97dad5623eb2.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
